<item>
            <title>[LU-11048] lctl pool commands have no man pages</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11048</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There is no man page for the &lt;tt&gt;lctl pool_new&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;pool_add&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;pool_remove&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;pool_destroy&lt;/tt&gt;, and &lt;tt&gt;pool_list&lt;/tt&gt; sub-commands.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Each command should get its own page like &lt;tt&gt;lustre/doc/lctl-pool_new.8&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
