                            <comment id="427399" author="JIRAUSER19233" created="Sun, 8 Sep 2024 21:11:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It seems the example in lctl-pool_add.8 and lctl-pool_new.8 is wrong, and the description fails to mention that the numbers of the OSTs must be in hexa form XXXX and proceeded by OST|fsname-OST&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;however if using a list of OSTs it is ok to do something like OST&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1-4&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="249366" author="adilger" created="Mon, 17 Jun 2019 03:34:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Man pages for &lt;tt&gt;lctl-pool_new.8&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;lctl-pool_add.8&lt;/tt&gt; were added in patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/34524&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/34524&lt;/a&gt; &quot;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-930&quot; title=&quot;Update or improvement to a Lustre man page, documentation, or messages&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-930&quot;&gt;LU-930&lt;/a&gt; doc: man pages for lctl pool_new, pool_add&lt;/tt&gt;&quot;, but &lt;tt&gt;pool_remove&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;pool_destroy&lt;/tt&gt;, and &lt;tt&gt;pool_list&lt;/tt&gt; are still missing.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
